My morning routine is majorly waking up immediately writing in my Gratitude journal and then stepping out of bed, having coffee and reading a book. This ‘Know Yourself’ Journal is gonna be my favourite addition in my routine. Thankyou @saltedcaramel.in 🫶🏼

Save the Date: 04.01.2026💍

From giggles in college corridors to building a life together, every moment has led us to this. Exactly a year from today, we’ll be walking down the aisle, starting a new chapter in our lives🤍 💍✨

Shot & Edited by @abys.angle @nikofwaste

1.9.24 💍  I planned an entire proposal trip to Udaipur for my girl, and she had no idea. Her girlfriends and I secretly got her ring size, and I began looking for the perfect proposal ring. Turns out, she already had a vision in mind—an intimate proposal, no crowds, just us, and an oval diamond with a gold band. I had only a short time to make it happen, but I found a brand that had exactly what I was looking for. In just 14 days, the ring was ready, and it arrived just 3 hours before our trip. I was panicking!

The day I planned to propose didn’t go as expected. It started raining, we had so much to do, and nothing seemed perfect—her outfit wasn’t on point, and there were too many people around. But I knew I had to do it before the weather got worse and she found the ring in my bag. Finally, at Udai Vilas, with my heart racing, I got down on one knee... and everything felt perfect, despite the chaos.

To my love, through every twist and turn, you’ve always been my constant. I can’t wait to spend forever with you. 💍❤️
